title: Time your work with Bubbletimer 1.0.0
description: Bubbletimer is a simple to use tool for keeping track of hours and minutes when working, studying, working out or whatever. Ever felt that you are losing money not counting those few minutes you waste on phonecalls or quick fixes to projects? Bubbletimer solves this problem just by letting you push START - PAUSE - STOP, your job is now logged! No configuration or learning needed.
